    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6378586/" class="title-link">气就是共振，频率的共振</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6378586"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u42033941-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sahaja/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">公益霎哈嘉瑜伽</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-11-05"
      class="main-meta">2013-11-05 13:45:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6378586_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  气就是共振，频率的共振。以现代科学的角度论证“气”。本书从中医的角度对人体的气与经络做出科学的解释，从不侧面论证了中医基本理论的合理性和现代医学的某些欠缺。现在发现霎哈嘉瑜伽静坐对身心带来的巨大改变都可以得到很好的解释。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
